    "/files/bulk-delete": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "files"
        ],
        "summary": "Bulk Delete Files",
        "description": "Delete N parsed files in one round-trip.\n\nEach file is processed independently using the same per-source subgraph\nwalk as the single-file DELETE — shared :Table / :Connection nodes stay\nintact. A failure on one file (unknown source, 404, Neo4j error) is\nrecorded in ``results`` for that file but doesn't abort the batch.",
